race.comment: ARTICULATING (1) raced below his best here last time in stronger but just missed prior in a 62. Milnes sticks aboard and he's well placed in this contest. Likes the course and trip and gets his chance. SHALHAVMUSIK (14) improved again winning this grade when backed off the map. Fitter again and keeps Holder. Just has to hold the form to feature. DODD (11) has an awkward gate but is busting to win and has been kept on the fresh side. Has to be considered as well. TESTA DEXTA (10) was plain two back, but the form around that is solid. Has an inside gate and Pannell sticking aboard is a positive.
